'''The Earliest Annals of Valinor''' is the sixth chapter of ''[[The Shaping of Middle-earth]]''.

==Synopsis==
This chapter details the events occurring in [[Valinor]] from The creation of all thing to approximately year 3000 of the [[Valar]], or roughly 30000 [[Years of the Sun|years of the sun]]. It details the creation of the world, the coming of [[elves]], the [[Chaining of Melkor|chaining]] of [[Morgoth]], his release and the death of the [[Two Trees of Valinor|trees]], the [[Exile of the Noldor|March of the Noldor]] begins, and the section ends with the arrival of [[Fingolfin]]'s forces in [[Middle-earth]] and the Rising of the [[sun]].
